Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.22,0:00:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在是幾點？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 是七點五十二分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.93,0:00:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比三年級的姐姐們還要遲 到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.75,0:00:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 祥子也變得了不起了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.96,0:00:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 完全忘記了 還是按平常的時間來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.20,0:00:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 八點才是集合時間 也還不算遲到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是祐巳她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.33,0:00:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.98,0:00:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.91,0:01:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳 這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.60,0:01:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼 是甚麼時候給的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.26,0:01:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.68,0:01:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該出手時就出手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.60,0:01:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.46,0:01:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開檢討會的時間越來越少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.72,0:01:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.66,0:01:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 別說那種話嘛 稍微給大家一點服務啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.73,0:01:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是甚麼時候 在哪裡進行的儀式？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.61,0:01:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「服務」是甚麼意思！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.58,0:01:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼我必須要給姐姐們服務啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.47,0:01:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就問祐巳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.51,0:01:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳這麼純真 會告訴我們的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.15,0:01:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.69,0:02:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼呀 那麼不想說嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.40,0:02:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那種無法言語的美妙回憶嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.35,0:02:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 祐巳太棒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.17,0:02:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想著你怎樣做才能擺脫你祥子姐姐的危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.47,0:02:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真是絕妙的時機啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.78,0:02:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了向祐巳的天生愚鈍表達敬意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次就放過她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 開始檢討會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.15,0:02:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在瑪莉亞的庭院裡的少女們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.71,0:03:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也帶著天使般無垢的笑容 穿越與身同高的門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.05,0:03:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覆蓋住純潔身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓裙子的摺痕亂掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.57,0:03:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓白色的水手服領結外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.76,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒緩的行走成了這裡的習俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私立莉莉安女學園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是少女的花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.39,0:04:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}黃薔薇革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.57,0:05:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有杯子了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 乾杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是慶祝校慶的成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.34,0:05:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著就是紀念祥子正式把祐巳變成自已的所有物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.20,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉著嘴 把嘴角擦一擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.69,0:05:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你不幫她擦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.59,0:05:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是白薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會連志摩子的嘴邊也照顧到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是志摩子的話我倒不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.66,0:05:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是祐巳的話我倒是很想幫她擦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁此機會 我先說清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要嬌縱我的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.97,0:05:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.11,0:05:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞部說這兩天想采訪一下由乃與令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.46,0:06:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞部嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和由乃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 說起來由乃同學呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨天開始就發燒不退 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.09,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發燒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.18,0:06:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說由乃同學的身體不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒真是那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.80,0:06:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說你與由乃在新聞部的全校問卷調查中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了最佳姐妹獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.43,0:06:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是正式的請求 所以不太好拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.62,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姐姐 由乃甚麼時候能來學校還不知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.30,0:06:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.60,0:06:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就只回答問卷調查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.33,0:06:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.65,0:06:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一來就讓她夢想幻滅了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她會讓我把念珠還給她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌心向上 伸出手來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.88,0:07:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你連早飯都沒吃就趕過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓自已太丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.83,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.15,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 這個「祥子大人」的稱呼也該停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的妹妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.83,0:07:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分清區別 好好地叫我「姐姐」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.51,0:07:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.51,0:07:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.55,0:08:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得「姐姐」這個詞對我來說太過奢侈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.42,0:08:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.74,0:08:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是外表 連文筆都這麼的完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.58,0:08:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.19,0:08:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別拿著上周那一期看得那麼入迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美 你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不趕快檢查一下次期的報道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.88,0:08:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到明天可也印不完啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.40,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到「最佳姐妹」獎的「莉莉安先生」支倉令大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.61,0:08:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與最想認為妹妹的島津由乃同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.32,0:08:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然采訪被拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻得到了問卷調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點寫報道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.50,0:09:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 能有一半像島津由乃一樣既天真又柔順就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 這個問卷調查沒搞錯吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.30,0:09:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.33,0:09:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學愛讀的書是池波正太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的話是「先手必勝」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興趣是觀看體育比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令同學愛讀的書是所有的少女小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的話是「真心」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興趣是編織衣物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像這兩個答卷應該顛倒一下才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.76,0:09:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是去確認一下比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.57,0:09:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅薔薇過後是黃薔薇嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許會很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 早退？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.37,0:09:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令前輩今天早退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.84,0:09:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.08,0:09:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明比賽就快到了 竟然還會早退…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.43,0:10:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學又還在請假休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.76,0:10:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人頭痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.02,0:10:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是黃薔薇大人的話 應該會知道妹妹們的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.18,0:10:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.13,0:10:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.94,0:10:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然叫住您真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.80,0:10:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想詢問一下令同學與由乃同學的興趣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.73,0:10:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興趣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接去問她們本人如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.56,0:10:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.05,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經問完了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.54,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起 耽誤您時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.42,0:10:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.44,0:10:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在河上乘一條小船漂流 而前方有一個大瀑布吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.68,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不衝下這個瀑布的話 就回不了我的家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.14,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手裡有漿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.12,0:10:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得該向哪邊劃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向哪邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.50,0:11:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的意思是說應該向上游劃還是該向下游劃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.83,0:11:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的 幹嘛對別人的意見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃薔薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.62,0:11:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.47,0:11:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.84,0:11:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來上學啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.85,0:11:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 從今天開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.31,0:11:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是休息了整整一星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.08,0:11:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然請別人幫忙抄了筆記 但還是很麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.96,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為最想認為妹妹的人也不是不可理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是二年級的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.20,0:11:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會想找一個像由乃同學般的一年級生作妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.56,0:11:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 沒甚麼事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學真是有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉上的表情又變來變去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.46,0:12:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學在心裡對我是甚麼印象呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.73,0:12:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 由乃同學的印象？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有點身體虛弱 很想給與保護的那種類型？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 倒不是說「身體虛弱」了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體虛弱也是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.24,0:12:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種「真是女孩子啊」的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.26,0:12:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待人禮貌 氣質沉靜 外表可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.50,0:12:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是我弟弟喜歡的類型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.59,0:12:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.32,0:12:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家裡穿上褶邊的圍裙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.30,0:12:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤烤餅乾 編編蕾絲的桌布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的飲品是奶茶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.48,0:12:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.33,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還養了一隻白色的貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.07,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這些全錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不是那種類型的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.94,0:13:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總被看成是那樣的女孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.60,0:13:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去薔薇館嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.47,0:13:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到姐姐來接我的時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得跟她一起回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令大人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.59,0:13:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 她不是有社團活動嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.16,0:13:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是我好久沒來上學了 所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐就是愛瞎操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.76,0:13:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.75,0:13:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上性格纖細
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.95,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是一點也看不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她在練劍道 所以看起來很強吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學真是毫不留情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.98,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是因為我們生下來就一直在一起 所以甚麼都很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐巳同學不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.09,0:13:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與令是表姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家也緊挨在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.62,0:13:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.56,0:14:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學從祥子大人那裡得到了念珠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.18,0:14:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是甚麼感覺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼感覺啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.02,0:14:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心跳加速嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.50,0:14:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.52,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們卻沒有那種感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.62,0:14:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道我與姐姐一直都在莉莉安讀書吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.10,0:14:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「上了高中後就成為姐妹」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.17,0:14:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間就像是有這種無言的默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.17,0:14:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入學式時 我因為身體不好沒有參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果姐姐就回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.00,0:14:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將念珠放在仍躺在床上的我的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有這樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是覺得是個很美的故事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.09,0:14:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 跟心跳加速是無緣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是先看了推理小說最後的結局一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意 只是一點牢騷而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何 就是想說給別人聽聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光聽著就夠了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足夠了 我到現在為止還沒有過這種朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.06,0:15:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.47,0:15:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以祐巳同學對我來說是很寶貴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐巳也在一起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.89,0:15:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我只是路過而已 馬上就要離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳同學 幹嘛 怕打擾我們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.78,0:15:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們又不是昨天或今天才成為姐妹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會粘得那麼緊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 粘得那麼緊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.24,0:15:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「粘得那麼緊」是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是甚麼大不了的事卻大聲斥責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是亂得很厲害的領結卻幫忙矯正
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還悄悄地交給糖球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.40,0:15:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了妹妹後 祥子真是相當開心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.60,0:15:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 令大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.52,0:15:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那麼回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.02,0:15:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳 去薔薇館的話酌情向姐姐們轉達一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.73,0:16:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在比賽結束前請讓我任性一下 很抱歉」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.55,0:16:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安 祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你訴說了這些後心情輕鬆多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.55,0:16:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情輕鬆？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學你有甚麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.84,0:16:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.75,0:16:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說黃薔薇的花蕾兩姐妹關係破裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.26,0:16:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在剛才啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.84,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學今天預約了醫生所以早退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後令大人也要跟著一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.79,0:16:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒道理讓令大人也一起早退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以由乃同學像是拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.68,0:16:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說計程車會來校門迎接 沒關係甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.59,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.53,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就在走向校門的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.30,0:17:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了「去」還是「不去」的反復爭論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.22,0:17:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由乃同學最後脾氣暴發了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.99,0:17:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.28,0:17:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是令大人說自已早已從班主任那裡\n得到早退的許可甚麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果被這件事激怒 由乃同學把念珠還了回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恰好又是在聖母瑪莉亞的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.07,0:17:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聖母瑪莉亞面前關係破裂…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係破裂與絕交不一樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說與離婚差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.94,0:17:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.19,0:17:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話又說回來 真擔心令大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在校園裡像亡靈一樣走來走去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.84,0:17:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟說夢話似的嘰哩咕嚕不知在講些甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.97,0:17:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快比賽了 沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令大人她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個早說呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐巳同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.42,0:17:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪邊呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.41,0:17:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 隨便找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.04,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.84,0:18:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.92,0:18:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐巳曾有想過將念珠還給祥子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 怎麼說呢 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.46,0:18:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你們才剛成為姐妹不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.57,0:18:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有這種想法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.71,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 請別給我隨意去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.84,0:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點 令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.75,0:18:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為黃薔薇的花蕾怎麼能這麼輕易就去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.75,0:18:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.25,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.55,0:18:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她在這裡搖搖晃晃地走來走去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而會添我們的麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.96,0:19:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「薔薇大人們一定不會坐視不理的」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我內心的某處確實是如此想的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抱太大的期望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.15,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.86,0:19:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟黃薔薇家族的事應該交給黃薔薇大人來解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.79,0:19:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為那個黃薔薇大人不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.07,0:19:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會像這樣來找姐姐們商量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.46,0:19:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是甚麼生與死的問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.55,0:19:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外人不插嘴家務事才是禮儀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.47,0:19:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過令如果希望的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倒是可以一起談談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.47,0:19:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們只是不想強行說教罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.52,0:19:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有可以幫得上忙的事嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.90,0:19:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.03,0:19:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇大人們的用心\n是想讓令大人能自已輕鬆地說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.58,0:20:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那個時候 我會找大家商量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在連我自已也很混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.09,0:20:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在我們就只算是多管閒事了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.32,0:20:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友 不就是為了幹這種吃虧的差事而存在的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.91,0:20:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 祥子與祐巳將令強拽到這裡來也許是對的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.10,0:20:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 令是搖搖擺擺的走來走去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不管對方是誰就像說夢話一樣嘮叨個不停吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.03,0:20:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.61,0:20:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 你做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.21,0:20:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說了後連自已都不知道 這可真的是重傷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志摩子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.20,0:21:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為令大人她們的事 好像引起了更嚴重的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.79,0:21:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更嚴重的問題？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.27,0:21:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除姐妹關係的學生出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還不是一個兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.08,0:21:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪同學真可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.59,0:21:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.81,0:21:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 只能這樣做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔦子同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.47,0:21:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你完全不明白發生了甚麼事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.83,0:21:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確不知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.51,0:21:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種號外出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.86,0:21:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.30,0:21:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在效仿由乃同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著一副悲壯的表情 將姐姐叫出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.02,0:21:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聖母瑪莉亞的面前將念珠交還
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.59,0:21:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼美雪同學不是被甩了 而是甩人的那一方了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.85,0:21:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自已把姐姐甩了還會哭得那麼厲害嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.53,0:21:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.63,0:21:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事還會增多的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.42,0:22:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.89,0:22:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打賭也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.44,0:23:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃同學將念珠交還 黃薔薇姐妹變得支離破碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.44,0:23:26.73,topfont,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：日語中「支離破碎」與「薔薇」同音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.73,0:23:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都變成薔薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.71,0:23:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是噱頭嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.09,0:23:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你竟能回應我的噱頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.22,0:23:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.89,0:23:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也開始語無倫次了
